<entry> A gnome-config path
</entry></row>
<row><entry align="right"><emphasis>Returns</emphasis> :</entry><entry> <literal>TRUE</literal> if everything went well, <literal>FALSE</literal> if the file
could not be written to for some reason.  <literal>FALSE</literal> is only returned
when a write was actually attempted and failed.
</entry></row>
</tbody></tgroup></informaltable></refsect2>
